AbstractTemporalLogicBaseVisitor
public interface AbstractTemporalLogicVisitor<T> extends org.antlr.v4.runtime.tree.ParseTreeVisitor<T>
This interface defines a complete generic visitor for a parse tree produced by AbstractTemporalLogicParser.
